wiki.summary: “Make You Mine” is a Grammy-nominated song released by Madison Beer on February 9th, 2024. On February 1st, 2024, Madison uploaded a video of her listening to a song in which you can hear the lyrics "I wanna feel", which were later confirmed to be lyrics to Make You Mine. On February 6th, 2024, Madison uploaded a video teasing her single, "Make You Mine" releasing that Friday. On February 7, she stated during an Instagram livestream that 'Make You Mine' and another single would be both part of a deluxe version for 'Silence Between Songs'. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: “Make You Mine” is a Grammy-nominated song released by Madison Beer on February 9th, 2024. On February 1st, 2024, Madison uploaded a video of her listening to a song in which you can hear the lyrics "I wanna feel", which were later confirmed to be lyrics to Make You Mine. On February 6th, 2024, Madison uploaded a video teasing her single, "Make You Mine" releasing that Friday. On February 7, she stated during an Instagram livestream that 'Make You Mine' and another single would be both part of a deluxe version for 'Silence Between Songs'. However the Supposed Deluxe Version was never released, and "Make You Mine" was included on her Third Studio Album "Locket", Set to be released in January 16 2026. Read more on Last.fm.
